snippet.title: Fall Guys: Ultimate Knockout - Season 4 Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description: Fall Guys: Ultimate Knockout continues its fun-filled fumble through time and space with the launch of Season 4! Astronauts, aliens and the funkiest looking Fall Guys this side of synthwave will bumble their way through a sci-fi inspired Season packed with seven new Rounds, plus oodles of challenges, costumes and delicious features. Dive in now!
